---
description: HermesProof STREAM coordination protocol
globs: handoffs/STREAM/**, .hermes3d_orchestrator/**
alwaysApply: true
---

Before code changes, read `handoffs/STREAM/STATE.md` and the active inbox.
Post `TASK_CLAIMED` before starting work, acquire HermesProof locks for every
file you will edit, and append evidence when the change is verified.

If another owner holds a lock, request handoff instead of editing. Never read
secret files, never force-push, never use `--no-verify`, and never push
directly to protected branches.
